      'Detects ageist assumptions and generational stereotyping in therapeutic interactions',
    icon: 'üë•',
    accent: 'red',
    examples:
      "Dismissing older adults' capacity, stereotyping younger clients' motivations",
  },
  {
    title: 'Mental Health Stigma Detection',
